data.description: Don't miss your opportunity to see this popular Vernon Hill model on a large corner lot located in the active 55+ community of Del Webb . This gorgeous 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a den/office cannot be missed. Upon entering the home through beautiful glass front door you are greeted by a spacious foyer/entry entry way. Just into the foyer the garage access door is to your immediate left and opens to an oversized 2 car garage that with an additioanl 4ft added as a builder upgrade. On your right side of the entry way are bedrooms 1 and 2 with the guest bathroom in between. All of the bedrooms in this home have upgraded engineered Pergo laminate flooring. You will also notice that all of the windows in this home have beautiful planation shutters. Once your past the foyer you are greeted by the open floor plan that offers views into the living room, kitchen, dining area, and even out to the screened in covered lanai. The kitchen offers luxurious granite counter tops, 42" maple Cabinets with crown molding, and an expansive kitchen island. Just off the kitchen is your interior laundry room, and walk in pantry. The kitchen also has a eat in breakfast space that has access to the lanai via an insulated slider door. The oversized living room offers plenty of entertaining space and even has an area for your formal dining room furniture. Just off the kitchen and living area is your den/office option which also offers the upgraded engineered Pergo laminate flooring. From the living room you can escape to the screened/covered lanai via the insulated Triple sliding glass doors. Your lanai offers plenty of space to relax and enjoy the morning coffee or a cocktail in the evening. A natural gas grill has a hookup on the lanai and the grill is included with the home. The master bedroom is in the back of the home for added privacy. The Master bath features two sinks, a beautiful soaking tub, a large glass walk in shower and a spacious walk in closet. Owners upgraded this home to maximize comfort and energy efficiency. These upgrades included the EFL energy package(insulated windows, doors, insulated slider doors, upgraded HVAC, and exterior vented Microwave). The exterior of home was recently painted and he home has gutters all around. The landscaping outside is absolutely stunning with beautiful palm trees and decorative concrete edging. The Hoa Fee of $257/month includes access to the magnificent 30.000+sqft Montecito clubhouse and yard maintenance. The Montecito clubhouse offers an expansive meeting area, sewing room, indoor swimming pool with disability access, spas, fitness center, outdoor pools, indoor walking track, and plenty of social clubs. The $396 semi-annual HOA fee includes the 24x7 staffed security gate and master association-owned private road maintenance. Located inside the Del Webb community is the recently renovated 18-hole  Heron Golf Club
